data.description: Welcome home to your dream townhome! Beautifully designed 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom Townhome. New roof 2023 and full remodel 2022 with newly renovated kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large island. Three bedrooms and a full bath upstairs. The lower level includes an additional fourth bedroom, kitchenette, full bath, and laundry. Half bath on the main level. Rear private parking for up to 2 cars. Basement studio space previously rented on Airbnb. Ideal for renting to single professionals/students.
